<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l22"><expan>Lantſchr<ex>eiber</ex></expan> beſant vnd Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief laſſen hören / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſprıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l23">Jr habt Jm <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> darvmb auch <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd hat vns geſagt </ab>
