<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Eberhart, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        habt von <add><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Trostpergs, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, und
                            <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>Ultfelds</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>
<expan>Lantschr<ex>eibers</ex></expan>, und <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Babemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
                        Trostperg und <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>Ültfeld<ex>er</ex></expan> bede <expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        nicht anheim sind; so ist <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> noch <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht.
                        Dann wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>
<expan>Lantschr<ex>eiber</ex></expan> besant und in
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief lassen hören und
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> spricht, ir habt im
                            <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> darumb auch
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und hat uns gesagt, daz Hans
                        Trostperg von <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Trostpergs
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan>
<expan>Ültfeld<ex>er</ex></expan> mit im yeczunden czü
                                <expan>Kiczing<ex>en</ex></expan> sein; und er main, daz sie das
                        richtig und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <add>einen</add> awstrag
                                <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllen. Ob sie
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> des nicht abtrügen, wenn sie
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> her heim <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        mant uns <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir sie
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czerede <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        wissen lassen. Und wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>q<ex>ua</ex>rta</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthoni.</ab>
</div>
